INSERT INTO `tbl_testimonial` VALUES (2,0,'JOSIE S','YgjFG-trip.png','https://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g1367591-d4550850-Reviews-Hotel_Seven_Star-Sauraha_Chitwan_District_Narayani_Zone_Central_Region.html','<p>\r\n	The room was very clean and nice. The staff was very helpful and friendly. Every wish was fulfilled. The organised tours were also great. Can only recommend the hotel.</p>\r\n',0,1,1,'Manchester, England','Trip Advisor',0,'offer/package-8','2024-08-26'),(3,0,'JIBAK','9FV2f-expedia.png','https://www.expedia.com/Sauraha-Hotels-Hotel-Seven-Star.h6469078.Hotel-Information','<p>\r\n	It was a very nice experience to stay at Hotel Seven Star. The Room, Environment, Service were excellent. The Restaurant was too good, Breakfast and Nepalese Thali was exceptional. Most importantly Hotel staffs, Tour guides were excellent. I lost my wedding ring during the Elephant safari and found it on the next day with the help of the Hotel Manager, Tour guides and Transport Service. It was impossible to find it without their honest effort and help. I would always recommend hotel Seven Star to anyone heading for Chitwan.</p>\r\n',5,2,1,'Kolkata, India','Expedia',0,'about-annapurna-view','2024-08-27'),(4,0,'SANJAY D','ghARi-trip.png','https://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g1367591-d4550850-Reviews-Hotel_Seven_Star-Sauraha_Chitwan_District_Narayani_Zone_Central_Region.html','<p>\r\n	Had wonderful experience in this property....nice ambiance...felt like home thanks to Ms. Dipsana madam for coordinating us in outside activities...overall nce stay..I will recommend this property to all my known...also suggest to visit tharu cultural program.</p>\r\n',4,3,1,'Los Angeles, California','Trip Advisor',0,'lounge-and-bar','2024-08-22');
